# Mental Health Tracker

## Project Overview
The Mental Health Tracker is a full-stack web application developed for monitoring and improving emotional well-being. The system helps users track daily mood, stress levels, sleep patterns, and personal notes in a secure and user-friendly environment.

The application encourages self-awareness and proactive mental health management through continuous monitoring and visualization.

